question:
Given the following code, what is the output if a `NumberFormatException` occurs? 

```java
try {
    // Code that may throw NumberFormatException
} catch (ArithmeticException e) {
    System.out.print("Arithmetic ");
} catch (NumberFormatException e) {
    System.out.print("NumberFormat ");
} catch (Exception e) {
    System.out.print("General ");
}
```

Consider the following code. Which statement about the `ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException` is true? 

```java
try {
    int[] arr = new int[5];
    arr[10] = 50; // Throws ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException
} catch (ArithmeticException | ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException e) {
    System.out.println("Math or Array error");
} catch (RuntimeException e) {
    System.out.println("General runtime error");
}
```
